VCATEntry.description: The VCATEntry schema defines an entry in a Virtual Channel Action Table.  A Virtual Channel is a mechanism used to create multiple, logical communication streams across a physical link.
VCATEntry.longDescription: This resource shall represent and entry of Virtual Channel Action Table in a Redfish implementation.
